# CampusRide — Full-Stack Implementation Plan

Build a secure, department-priority-based ride-sharing platform for Shobhit University.
**Backend**: Java 21 / Spring Boot 3.x, PostgreSQL+PostGIS, Redis, WebSockets.
**Frontend**: React 18, Redux Toolkit, Material UI, Tailwind CSS, react-leaflet.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **PostGIS Dependency** — PostgreSQL must have the PostGIS extension installed. The schema migration will run `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS postgis;`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Redis Required** — A running Redis instance is needed for real-time location caching. Default: `localhost:6379`.

> [!WARNING]
> **Email Lock-in** — Registration is restricted to `@shobhituniversity.ac.in` emails. Ensure this is the correct domain before we proceed.

