### 10. Redux Toolkit — Slices

#### [NEW] [features/auth/authSlice.js](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/features/auth/authSlice.js)
| State field | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| user | Object / null | `{id, name, email, role, dept, course, year, verified}` |
| token | String / null | JWT stored in localStorage + slice |
| loading | Boolean | API call in flight |
| error | String / null | Last error message |

**Async thunks**: `registerUser`, `loginUser`, `loadUserFromToken`
- On login success: store JWT in `localStorage`, decode claims, set `user`.
- On 401/403: clear token, redirect to `/login`.

#### [NEW] [features/rides/ridesSlice.js](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/features/rides/ridesSlice.js)
| State field | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| availableRides | Array | Search results (with `matchScore`) |
| myRides | Array | Rides created by current user |
| myRequests | Array | Requests sent by passenger |
| currentRide | Object / null | Selected ride detail |
| loading / error | — | Standard flags |

**Async thunks**: [searchRides({lat, lng})](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride/src/main/java/com/campusride/controller/RideController.java#31-43), [createRide](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride/src/main/java/com/campusride/service/RideService.java#30-65), `fetchMyRides`, [sendRequest](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride/src/main/java/com/campusride/service/RideRequestService.java#29-64), `acceptRequest`, `confirmRequest`

