**Async thunks**: [fetchHistory(rideId, page)](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/components/chat/ChatBubble.jsx#19-24), [markAsRead(messageId)](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride/src/main/java/com/campusride/service/ChatService.java#51-58)
