### 17. Routing & Layout

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/App.jsx)
```jsx
// Route structure
<Routes>
  <Route path="/login"     element={<LoginPage />} />
  <Route path="/register"  element={<RegisterPage />} />

  {/* Protected — requires JWT */}
  <Route element={<ProtectedRoute />}>
    <Route path="/"             element={<DashboardPage />} />
    <Route path="/dashboard"    element={<DashboardPage />} />
    <Route path="/rides/create" element={<CreateRidePage />} />
    <Route path="/rides/search" element={<SearchRidePage />} />
    <Route path="/rides/:id"    element={<RideDetailPage />} />
    <Route path="/trip/:id"     element={<ActiveTripPage />} />
  </Route>

  {/* Admin — requires ADMIN role */}
  <Route element={<ProtectedRoute requiredRole="ADMIN" />}>
    <Route path="/admin"        element={<AdminDashboard />} />
  </Route>
</Routes>
```

#### [NEW] [components/common/ProtectedRoute.jsx](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/components/common/ProtectedRoute.jsx)
- Reads `token` + `user.role` from Redux
- If not authenticated → `<Navigate to="/login" />`
- If `requiredRole` set and doesn't match → `<Navigate to="/" />`

