### 18. WebSocket Hook

#### [NEW] `hooks/useWebSocket.js`
- Creates a single STOMP client on mount (`ws://localhost:8080/ws` + SockJS)
- Exposes: [subscribe(destination, callback)](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/utils/websocketService.js#28-41), [send(destination, body)](file:///d:/haykhathon/campusride-frontend/src/utils/websocketService.js#42-52), `connected`
- Used by `ActiveTripPage` (location) and `ChatWindow` (messages)

