### Manual Verification
1. Start server: `cd d:\haykhathon\campusride && mvnw spring-boot:run`
2. `POST /api/auth/register` with valid `@shobhituniversity.ac.in` email → 200
3. Register with invalid email → 400
4. `POST /api/auth/login` → JWT token returned
5. Create ride using JWT → 201
6. Search rides near a coordinate → results sorted by match score
7. WebSocket: connect `/ws`, subscribe `/topic/ride/{id}`, send location → broadcast received
8. Chat: send message via `/app/chat/send` → appears in `/topic/chat/{rideId}` and persists in DB

